				</div>
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div role="note" class="hatnote">This article is about the nation of Samoa. For the geographical region, see <a href="/wiki/Samoan_Islands" title="Samoan Islands">Samoan Islands</a>. For the Samoan United States territory, see <a href="/wiki/American_Samoa" title="American Samoa">American Samoa</a>. For other uses, see <a href="/wiki/Samoa_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Samoa (disambiguation)">Samoa (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
